Let’s go to beach beach (and have banana-pancakes)... 🎶☀️🤙🏼🥞 In these times we all crave some fresh air and open wides but we also need to be responsible and make sure to keep a social distance. Therefore @mariannesoegaardv and I drove out of the city and out to the coast to enjoy the warm sun and listen to the waves - and have some banana pancakes. I can strongly reccommend that combination. 🤙🏼☀️🌱🌊🏖🥞
